# xUCP Free
 In this User Control Panel, it is a completely new development. The xUCP is for all Roleplay Projects!
 
xUCP Free (Open Source) Readme
(C) 2022 DerStr1k3r.de
https://derstr1k3r.de
https://discord.gg/xg5mnYUWch


Requirements for xUCP Free:

  1. MySQL servers
  2. Web server (XAMPP is not supported!)
  3. Php 8.x or newer

Features of the xUCP Free:

  1. CSRF Login & CSRF Register System
  2. Staff Tools ( User Changer, Playerlist, News Creator, Rules Manager, Whitelist Manager, Keyboard Manager )
  3. Language System ( English & German )
  4. Support system
  5. Edit profile
  6. My character
  7. Site Settings
  8. Clients & Servers


best regards

DerStr1k3r
